OOC: alrighty we can start again
         Quilldart ducked and dodge one missle but took a missle to the arm. 
It was blown off half way up his arm. The two broken bots seemed to be even. 
He saw his leader retreating, so he had to follow.  He jeted off towards the 
predacon base sending a comm to the bot, "YOu have earned my respect..not 
something many can say...I look forward to our next meeting. It shall be 
soon." He had to hurry he would enter stasis lock soon.

--part1_83.23a7e82e.2b086541_boundary
